<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>Verifikasi Email SILAPOR</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: 'Inter', Arial, sans-serif;
        background: #f6f6f6;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
      }
      .container {
        max-width: 480px;
        margin: 40px auto;
        background: #fff;
        border-radius: 16px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(34,197,94,0.08);
        padding: 32px;
        color: #222;
      }
      .header {
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 24px;
      }
      .logo {
        width: 64px;
        height: 64px;
        margin-bottom: 12px;
      }
      .title {
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: #16a34a;
        margin-bottom: 8px;
      }
      .content {
        font-size: 1rem;
        margin-bottom: 24px;
      }
      .verify-btn {
        display: inline-block;
        background: linear-gradient(90deg,#22c55e,#16a34a);
        color: #fff;
        font-weight: 600;
        padding: 12px 32px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-size: 1rem;
        margin-bottom: 16px;
      }
      .footer {
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        color: #888;
        text-align: center;
        margin-top: 24px;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <img src="https://i.ibb.co/6WZyJ2g/logo.png" alt="SILAPOR Logo" class="logo" />
        <div class="title">Verifikasi Email Anda</div>
      </div>
      <div class="content">
        <h3>Halo <%= nama %>,</h3>
        <p>Terima kasih telah mendaftar di SILAPOR Universitas Andalas.<br>
        Untuk mengaktifkan akun Anda, silakan klik tombol di bawah ini:</p>
      </div>
      <div style="text-align:center;">
        <a href="<%= verifyLink %>" class="verify-btn">Verifikasi Akun</a>
      </div>
      <div class="footer">
        Jika tombol tidak berfungsi, salin dan buka link berikut di browser Anda:<br>
        <a href="<%= verifyLink %>" style="color:#16a34a;word-break:break-all;"> <%= verifyLink %> </a>
        <br><br>
        Salam,<br>
        Tim SILAPOR Unand
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
